    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required credibility level. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged and accepted because the COU is limited to ASTM F1717 standard conditions and no extrapolation beyond those conditions is claimed. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-specified quantitative acceptance bounds (E/uval < 1.96; percent difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is assessed as credible for the stated COU at Medium assurance level.",
